name: Emoji 1997
description:
Original Softbank JP Emoji set from 1997.


The set contains 180 pixel-art icons, 90x2 with light and dark version.


All icons were restored with vector graphics and compiled as components to be used as a part of interface or graphic work.


All the rights belong to Softbank JP.

You can find more info about Emoji 1997 set here.
